snippet.title: CTGP Nitro - Release Trailer (Ver 1.0.0) NEW Features!
snippet.description:
CTGP Nitro is a Mario Kart DS ROM Hack that, instead of replacing existing tracks, adds new ones!
It will be updated over time to add new CTs, and other extra content. As of Version 1.0 there are 56 extra tracks to choose from.

Download:
https://dswiki.garhoogin.com/ctgp-n/

Mirror: 
https://gamebanana.com/mods/289453


Want to play CTGP Nitro online? Please read the read me included with CTGP Nitro for more information.

This trailer's music was made by the talented musician @VGM Haven!
Trailer made by @rocoloco321
